===Noun===
'''supper''' (''plural:'' [[suppers]])

#[[food]] consumed before going to bed.
#[[dinner]] eaten at night, rather than at [[lunchtime]].
#A [[drinker]], especially one who drinks slowly (i.e., one who [[sup]]s).

